#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:73
msgid "3. submit_with_ack 与本地订单"
msgstr "3. submit_with_ack 與本地訂單"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:75
msgid "**与风控拒单不同**：风控在更前面，**不入订单表**（见 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle`）。"
msgstr "**與風控拒單不同**：風控在更前面，**不入訂單表**（見 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle`）。"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:77
msgid ""
"`submit_with_ack` 同步返回券商是否**受理**委托。下表仅描述**受理阶段**本地订单与 `broker_order_id` "
"的对应关系；成交进度见 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle` 状态表。"
msgstr ""
"`submit_with_ack` 同步返回券商是否**受理**委託。下表僅描述**受理階段**本地訂單與 `broker_order_id` "
"的對應關係；成交進度見 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle` 狀態表。"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:79
msgid ""
"**各列含义**：**受理结果**为 ACK 中的 accepted 语义；**本地订单**为订单表状态走向；**broker_order_id** "
"为是否回写券商委托号。"
msgstr ""
"**各列含義**：**受理結果**爲 ACK 中的 accepted 語義；**本地訂單**爲訂單表狀態走向；**broker_order_id** "
"爲是否回寫券商委託號。"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:81
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：订单 `rejected` 且 broker 号为空 → 查「accepted=False」行；有 broker 号但长期不成交 → "
"查状态表与 `poll_fills`。"
msgstr ""
"**如何使用**：訂單 `rejected` 且 broker 號爲空 → 查「accepted=False」行；有 broker 號但長期不成交 → "
"查狀態表與 `poll_fills`。"

