msgid "未 `connect` 就 `submit` / `poll_fills`：应得到明确错误，而非静默失败"
msgstr "未 `connect` 就 `submit` / `poll_fills`：應得到明確錯誤，而非靜默失敗"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:108
msgid "`cancel` 未知委托号：应稳定返回「未撤成」"
